      "title": "Auto-Improving Software",
      "preview_text": "Coding agents have changed how we build software. Now they're changing how we improve it. Today I'll share an agent platform that coding agents build, run, and improve on their own.\nThe entire agent",
      "cover_media": {
        "id": "QXBpTWVkaWE6DAAFCgABHIDEEGibUAAKAAIAAAAAAJ3uAgAA",
